律黎, 唔好同我拗<br />\n2. 功能組別選民請舉手<br />\n工程界<br />\n註冊的專業工程師及有權在香港工程師學會的大會上表決的該會會員<br />\n勞工界<br />\n在過去 12 個月運作的工會都可以登記成為勞工界選民 我知好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飲食界<br />\n選民包括所有食物業牌照的持有人<br />\n體育、演藝、文化及出版界<br />\n體育、藝術、電影、出版或電視相關團體或公司的代表(之前有人講過體育會)<br />\n其他果D 可能都太遲...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbefaff84c428845e6b2ab9309b679b0d47d7e18","tid":1756142,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:46:07.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae145f5debcfe1f998e8e7f7eb6fa412f998a66","tid":1756142,"uid":168250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:50:28.000Z","msg":"雖然好撚憎親共派嗰啲撚屎蛇齋餅糭 但真係對付老人家嘅好方法 你喺區會大會細會開咗幾多會 做咗幾多野 啲人係睇唔到 反而派吓野露吓面俾啲甜頭咁啲老野就覺得你做到野 所以呢啲細節野一定要做 仲要學親共派咁做足佢"},{"pid":"a11825ab6d96a145bcfa55bfdbb472075a1a974c","tid":1756142,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:53:15.000Z","msg":"黃色文具鋪"},{"pid":"1d3b413a3069a38c487c7a6bd3e9ac652c05a11a","tid":1756142,"uid":12444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:03:50.000Z","msg":"最簡單可以寫下揮春、派下小禮物咁......其實最緊要都係多d葡頭 同老人家9up下 佢地就會記得你"},{"pid":"afa15100d439bc00afab7b6ba1aa3d627f122d34","tid":1756142,"uid":54715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:31:04.000Z","msg":"早排見個義工用候選人名同公仔既環保斜孭袋幾靚<br />\n勁想問佢點樣攞，幫佢宣傳下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2905f3924bc7c8245ad36b189648732b5d5b17e9","tid":1756142,"uid":128558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afa15100d439bc00afab7b6ba1aa3d627f122d34","tid":1756142,"uid":54715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-2